lead_paragraph: German soccer great Franz Beckenbauer underwent open heart bypass surgery on Saturday in an operation scheduled long before Swiss authorities opened criminal proceedings against him last week, Germany's Bild newspaper reported Monday.

headline.print_headline: German Soccer Icon Beckenbauer Has Bypass Surgery-Bild
